data.description: This property has the potential to be a great investment or to be your family home! This house has 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with one of the bedrooms having a private entrance which could be used as the mother-in-law suite. It has an open concept kitchen with granite countertops, electric stove and refrigerator. This house comes with a huge backyard where you can customize your very own retreat which could include a pool. It sits on a prime location near BISCAYNE BLVD/US1 where you can find all your shopping options such as Aventura Mall, Ball Harbor, many restaurants and delis, as well as the beach. It is 20 minutes from downtown Miami. The property is SOLD AS IS. *All showings must be accompanied by an agent and an appointment to be made 24 hours prior to the showings.
